meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( "EBAN"."BANFN" ) = 1 THEN 'No PR No.' ELSE "EBAN"."ESTKZ_TEXT" END AS "#{PRCreationIndicator}"

axis0.name: #{PRCreationIndicator}
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN ISNULL(PU_LAST("EKKO","EBAN"."BANFN")) = 1 THEN 'No PR No.' 
    ELSE  PU_LAST(EKKO,"EBAN"."ESTKZ_TEXT")
END

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN ISNULL ( "EKPO"."MATNR" ) = 1 THEN 'w/o Material No.' ELSE 'w/ Material No.' END AS "#{\"EKPO\".\"MATNR\"}" FORMAT "%"

axis0.name: #{"EKPO"."MATNR"}
axis0.text:
CASE    
    WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."MATNR") = 1
    THEN 'w/o Material No.' 
    ELSE 'w/ Material No.'  
END

meta.expressionLhs: CASE WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) > 0 AND PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) IN ( 'B' ) THEN 'Automated' WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) > 0 AND ISNULL ( PU_LAST ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) ) = 1 THEN 'No User Type' WHEN PU_COUNT ( "EKPO" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" , "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Create Purchase Requisition Item' ) > 0 THEN 'Manual' ELSE 'No Purchase Requisition' END AS "#{\"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES\".\"USER_TYPE\"}"

axis0.name: #{"_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE"}
axis0.text:
CASE 
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>" = '<%=create_purchase_requisition_activity%>' )> 0
    AND PU_LAST("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>" = '<%=create_purchase_requisition_activity%>') IN (<%=auto_user_type%>)
    THEN 'Automated'
    
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>" = '<%=create_purchase_requisition_activity%>' )> 0 
    
    AND ISNULL(PU_LAST("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."USER_TYPE", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>" = '<%=create_purchase_requisition_activity%>')) = 1
    THEN 'No User Type'
    
    WHEN PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_<%=language%>" = '<%=create_purchase_requisition_activity%>' )> 0
    THEN 'Manual'
    ELSE 'No Purchase Requisition'
END
